		<title>Highsoft nominated for Nordic Startup Awards</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.highcharts.com/docs/maps/2-articles/news/136-highsoft-nominated-for-nordic-startup-awards"/>
		<published>2014-05-14T12:30:23+00:00</published>
		<updated>2014-05-14T12:30:23+00:00</updated>
		<id>http://www.highcharts.com/docs/maps/2-articles/news/136-highsoft-nominated-for-nordic-startup-awards</id>
		<author>
			<name>Super User</name>
			<email>torstein@highsoft.com</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;feed-description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #141823; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, 'lucida grande', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.31999969482422px;&quot;&gt;We have been nominated for Nordic Startup Awards! First, national winners will be picked. To to win the Norwegian nomination we need your help. Go to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://app.socialcee.com/controls/pagemodules/imageuploadcompetition/fbshareitem.aspx?id=988961&amp;amp;pagemoduleid=8670&quot;&gt;Startup Awards voting page&lt;/a&gt;, select country (Norway) and category (Startup of the year), then vote for Highsoft. Thank you!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
