&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;images/stories/articles/cloudsave.png&quot; alt=&quot;cloud-save&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Logged in users can also set a base version for their charts. A base version is a special version that will&amp;nbsp;be shown if no version are specified.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Examples:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
