&lt;h3&gt;Feedback&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Please give feedback, bug reports or general discussion in our &lt;a href=&quot;http://forum.highcharts.com/highcharts-cloud-f13/&quot;&gt;forum section for Highcharts Cloud&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
